Adaptation;;85;;90;;R;;Nicolas Cage is Charlie Kaufman, a confused L.A. screenwriter overwhelmed by feelings of inadequacy, sexual frustration, self-loathing, and by the screenwriting ambitions of his freeloading twin brother Donald (Nicolas Cage). While struggling to adapt "The Orchid Thief," by Susan Orlean (Meryl Streep), Kaufman's life spins from pathetic to bizarre. The lives of Kaufman, Orlean's book, become strangely intertwined as each one's search for passion collides with the others'.;;Comedy,Drama;;Spike Jonze;;2002;;Nicolas Cage,Meryl Streep,Chris Cooper,Tilda Swinton,Cara Seymour,Brian Cox,Judy Greer,Maggie Gyllenhaal,Ron Livingston,Jay Tavare,Stephen Tobolowsky,Peter Jason,Curtis Hanson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1118700-adaptation